The noun is from {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|pleye|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term/t|ang|plæġ}}, {{term/t|ang|pleġa}}, {{term/t|ang|plæġa||play, quick motion, movement, exercise; (athletic) sport, game; festivity, drama; battle; gear for games, an implement for a game; clapping with the hands, applause}}, deverbative of {{term/t|ang|pleġian||to play}}; see above.

